Symbols pay anywhere on the screen. The total number of the same symbol on the
screen at the end of a spin determines the value of the win.

This is the SCATTER symbol.
SCATTER symbol appears on all reels.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning
symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are
replaced with symbols coming from above.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.

An extra reel showing 5 random multiplier symbols, drops at every spin. All wins in the game are multiplied by the bottom most multiplier from this reel. After every tumble, the multipliers on this reel tumble down one position.
Possible mutlipliers are: x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, x6, x8, x10, x12, x15, x20, x25, x50, x100, x250 or x500.

Hit 4, 5 or 6 SCATTER symbols to trigger the FREE SPINS feature and win 10, 12 or 14 free spins respectively.
During the FREE SPINS round, the minimum multiplier possible on the MULTIPLIER REEL is x2.
Hit 4, 5 or 6 SCATTER symbols during the round to retrigger the feature and win 5, 8 or 10 additional free spins.
Special reels are in play during the feature.

The maximum win amount is limited to 1,0000x bet in both base game and free spins. If the total win of a FREE SPINS
round reaches 1,0000x bet the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining free spins are forfeited.

The FREE SPINS ROUND can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet.
When buying the free spins round 4, 5 or 6 SCATTERS are guaranteed to hit randomly on the triggering spin.
